>\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470387</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6858dc406c925c7e53f90a5023807734a925c8a0","tid":1471511,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:37:07.000Z","msg":"請幫推"},{"pid":"608290e8e3e98891e96335528c6430864affa209","tid":1471511,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/68945174_10156523987502849_5604470728259796992_n_ECg95_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F68945174_10156523987502849_5604470728259796992_n_ECg95_1200x0.jpg&h=ad194b3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0183db15597b18dd9dfe2cc3bfaaa5faf5289130","tid":1471511,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:45:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"918961cbc26435e2bca89bc6ba2e8ab732e75152","tid":1471511,"uid":292151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:47:55.000Z","msg":"你可以哭泣，但不要洩氣！"},{"pid":"c8f64254391968bcd508d45b2a92a01429787165","tid":1471511,"uid":2634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:54:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>「你可以哭泣，但不要洩氣。你可以悲傷，但是不要放棄，因為明天起來，我們要像過去四年一樣的勇敢，心裏充滿着希望。因為，我們必須勇敢地扛起這個國家的責任，我們必須樂觀地，繼續為台灣這塊土地打拼。」<br />\n「有一天，我們會再回來，我們不會放棄。」<br />\n---2012年蔡英文敗選後發言---</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"fdbf150025b33022bee9f0e9c42e1efdcf4d4f8a","tid":1471511,"uid":210280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:56:14.000Z","msg":"請不要說推，說<br />\n721 811<br />\n818我會上街<br />\n不分化 不割蓆<br />\n唔做捉鬼敢死隊"},{"pid":"a6d9667e6708439cfe0706222e221e10b828aab8","tid":1471511,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdbf15002